statements.sql: select column_name as `column_name` from information_schema.columns where table_schema = 'foodtiger' and table_name = 'roles'

select `roles`.*, `model_has_roles`.`model_id` as `pivot_model_id`, `model_has_roles`.`role_id` as `pivot_role_id`, `model_has_roles`.`model_type` as `pivot_model_type` from `roles` inner join `model_has_roles` on `roles`.`id` = `model_has_roles`.`role_id` where `model_has_roles`.`model_id` = 1 and `model_has_roles`.`model_type` = 'App\User'

select * from `users` where exists (select * from `roles` inner join `model_has_roles` on `roles`.`id` = `model_has_roles`.`role_id` where `users`.`id` = `model_has_roles`.`model_id` and `model_has_roles`.`model_type` = 'App\User' and `roles`.`id` in (3)) and (`active` = 1 and `working` = 1)

select `status`.*, `order_has_status`.`order_id` as `pivot_order_id`, `order_has_status`.`status_id` as `pivot_status_id`, `order_has_status`.`user_id` as `pivot_user_id`, `order_has_status`.`created_at` as `pivot_created_at`, `order_has_status`.`comment` as `pivot_comment` from `status` inner join `order_has_status` on `status`.`id` = `order_has_status`.`status_id` where `order_has_status`.`order_id` in (613) order by `order_has_status`.`id` desc limit 1

select `status`.*, `order_has_status`.`order_id` as `pivot_order_id`, `order_has_status`.`status_id` as `pivot_status_id`, `order_has_status`.`user_id` as `pivot_user_id`, `order_has_status`.`created_at` as `pivot_created_at`, `order_has_status`.`comment` as `pivot_comment` from `status` inner join `order_has_status` on `status`.`id` = `order_has_status`.`status_id` where `order_has_status`.`order_id` = 613 order by `order_has_status`.`id` desc limit 1
select count(*) as aggregate from `status` inner join `order_has_status` on `status`.`id` = `order_has_status`.`status_id` where `order_has_status`.`order_id` = 613 and `status_id` = 5
